<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#TimeIndexedRelation> rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Situation> ,
                                                                                            [ owl:intersectionOf ( <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Situation>
