                                                                                            ] .


###  http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#TimeInterval
<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#TimeInterval> rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Region> ,
                                                                                     [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
